<plot>Six kids - three hard core street kids who have no value for human life, and three kids who love life yet are terminally ill - share their lives together for one week. The dramatic values, true-life stories and unavoidable moral and ethical lessons are so gripping and natural that parents and children who watch may literally find their lives transformed - a life changing educational tool.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?017220</url></doc>
